      "index": "ad",
      "text": "Why effective_at alone is not enough\n- a late entry can be written with an earlier effective_at\n- multiple entries may share the same effective_at\n- account_version gives the exact ledger cut for one snapshot\n- this prevents mismatches between balance and displayed entries",
      "fontSize": 18,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 18,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Why effective_at alone is not enough\n- a late entry can be written with an earlier effective_at\n- multiple entries may share the same effective_at\n- account_version gives the exact ledger cut for one snapshot\n- this prevents mismatches between balance and displayed entries",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "autoResize": true
